      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  w-b16-dec-b16-bin          pic  x(16)                  .
           05  w-b16-dec-b16-bin-r redefines
               w-b16-dec-b16-bin.
               10  w-b16-dec-b16-ele occurs 16
                                          pic  9(01)                  .
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * Numero decodificato, intero senza decimali            *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  w-b16-dec-b16-dec          pic  9(05)                  .
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * Comodi                                                *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  w-b16-dec-b16-max          pic  9(02)      value  16   .
           05  w-b16-dec-b16-elv          pic  9(01)      value   2   .
           05  w-b16-dec-b16-inx          pic  9(02)                  .
           05  w-b16-dec-b16-xel          pic  9(02)                  .
           05  w-b16-dec-b16-res          pic  9(05)                  .
           05  w-b16-dec-b16-add          pic  9(05)                  .

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Work per subroutines di somma 'xor' tra binari a 16 bit   *
