                                          pic  9(01)                  .
           05  w-b16-xor-b16-bi2          pic  x(16)                  .
           05  w-b16-xor-b16-bi2-r redefines
               w-b16-xor-b16-bi2.
               10  w-b16-xor-b16-el2 occurs 16
                                          pic  9(01)                  .
